---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Banner -->
  <div class="main-banner page-banner">
    <div class="img-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="inner-content"> <span class="top-heading">Email</span>
              <h1>Professional and Secure Email Hosting Solutions for Businesses</h1>
              <h3>Reliable, secure, and scalable email hosting for businesses and professionals.</h3>
              <ul class="banner-list icon">
                <li><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2"></i>Secure Data Encryption</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up me-2"></i>99.9% Uptime Guarantee</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-virus me-2"></i>Spam and Virus Protection</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-inboxes me-2"></i>Easy Integration & Management</li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-3"> <span>Starts at just</span> <sup>৳</sup> <strong>503.99</strong> <small>/mo</small> </h4>
              <div class="inline-btns mt-3"> <a class="btns one" href="">Get Started Now<i class="far fa-arrow-right"></i></a> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/enterprise-email.png" alt="Web Hosting" width="500"> </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Plan Section -->
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-header center gap-bottom">
            <h2>Choose Your Plan</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="swiper swiper-plans-two">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/database.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>Silver </h3>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
                  <h6><del>৳25.25</del> / Month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 16.20 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Offer</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 2 GB Disk Space</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-tachometer-alt-slow"></i> Unlimited Bandwidth </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-browser"></i> cPanel Control Panel </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-server"></i> 6GB Memory</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-database"></i> 10 Hosted Domains</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i>LiteSpeed Web Server </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL Certificate</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/server.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>Gold</h3>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
                  <h6><del>৳25.25</del> / Month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 16.20 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Offer</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 2 GB Disk Space</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-tachometer-alt-slow"></i> Unlimited Bandwidth </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-browser"></i> cPanel Control Panel </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-server"></i> 6GB Memory</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-database"></i> 10 Hosted Domains</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i>LiteSpeed Web Server </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL Certificate</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="plans-design-one"> <img src="/images/servers.png" alt="icon" class="icon">
                  <h3>Platinum</h3>
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
                  <h6><del>৳25.25</del> / Month</h6>
                  <h4> <sup>৳</sup> 16.20 <small>/year</small> <span class="badge-plan">Offer</span> </h4>
                  <a class="btns three" href="">Select Plan</a>
                  <ul>
                    <li><i class="ri-hard-drive-2-line"></i> 2 GB Disk Space</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-tachometer-alt-slow"></i> Unlimited Bandwidth </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-browser"></i> cPanel Control Panel </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-server"></i> 6GB Memory</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-database"></i> 10 Hosted Domains</li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-globe"></i>LiteSpeed Web Server </li>
                    <li><i class="fal fa-lock"></i> Free SSL Certificate</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>Email Hosting Features</h2>
            <p>Secure, reliable, fast, scalable, encrypted, spam-free, cloud-based, and user-friendly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-lg-5 gy-4">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/gmail.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Gmail</h4>
              <p>Gmail offers secure, fast, and user-friendly email services with spam protection, cloud storage, and accessibility.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/calendar.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Calendar</h4>
              <p>Calendar helps schedule events, set reminders, manage tasks, sync devices, and organize daily activities efficiently.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/meet.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Meet</h4>
              <p>Meet enables secure video conferencing, screen sharing, real-time collaboration, chat, and seamless team communication.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/docs.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Docs</h4>
              <p>Docs allows real-time collaboration, cloud storage, editing, sharing, formatting, and secure document management online.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/sheets.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Sheets</h4>
              <p>Sheets offers real-time collaboration, data analysis, charts, automation, cloud storage, and secure spreadsheet management.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/slides.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Slides</h4>
              <p>Slides enables real-time collaboration, creative presentations, templates, animations, cloud storage, and seamless sharing options.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/drive.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Drive</h4>
              <p>Drive provides secure cloud storage, file sharing, backups, collaboration, accessibility, and seamless device synchronization.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/forms.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>forms</h4>
              <p>Forms enables easy survey creation, data collection, real-time collaboration, customization, analytics, and seamless integration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="service-three text-center">
            <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/chat.png" alt="image"> </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h4>Chat</h4>
              <p>Chat enables real-time messaging, file sharing, collaboration, group chats, notifications, and secure communication.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap bg1">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Bussiness Hosting Extra Benefits</h2>
            <ul class="list-check">
              <li>Reliability and Uptime</li>
              <li>Enhanced Security</li>
              <li>Performance Optimization</li>
              <li>Dedicated Support</li>
              <li>Compliance and Regulatory Requirements</li>
              <li>Customization and Control</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/buss_mail1.png" alt="Reseller Hosting" width="500"> </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4 align-items-center flex-lg-row-reverse">
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>What is Email Hosting ?</h2>
            <p>Email hosting is a service that provides custom email addresses using a domain name. It ensures security, reliability, and professional communication with advanced features like spam protection, encryption, and cloud storage, making it ideal for businesses and organizations. <br>
              Email hosting is a specialized service that allows users to create and manage professional email accounts linked to their domain. It offers enhanced security, high uptime, and advanced management tools, ensuring seamless communication and data protection for businesses and individuals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="text-center text-lg-start"> <img src="/images/email-img.webp" alt="Reseller Hosting" width="500"> </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap ">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 bg1 support">
          <div class="row g-4 align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
              <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Our Solution Support Center</h2>
                <p>Our Solution Support Center provides expert assistance, troubleshooting, and guidance for seamless technical support.</p>
                <div class="mt-3">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/talk.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">0212 909 9656</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/support2.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">24*7 Support</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/customer.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">Talk to customer</label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/support-center.png" alt="Reseller Hosting"> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Get the answers to frequently asked questions about our premium hosting service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <ul class="accordion">
            <li>
              <h5> How will purchasing Business Email benefit me? </h5>
              <p>Purchasing Business Email offers secure communication, professional features, collaboration tools, and ample storage, enhancing efficiency and establishing a credible and reliable online business presence.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> Which Email Clients and protocols are supported? </h5>
              <p>Our Business Email supports popular email clients like Outlook, Thunderbird, and mobile devices, using standard protocols such as IMAP, POP3, and SMTP for flexible and accessible communication.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> How do I use my Webmail Interface? </h5>
              <p>Access your webmail interface by logging into your email hosting account. Navigate through the user-friendly interface to manage emails, contacts, calendars, and settings effortlessly.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> Which mobile phones can I access my mail from? </h5>
              <p>You can access your mail from a variety of mobile phones, including iOS and Android devices. Simply configure your email account using the standard IMAP or POP3 settings.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> What is the space provided per Email Account? </h5>
              <p>The space provided per email account depends on the hosting plan. Generally, it ranges from 5GB to unlimited storage, ensuring ample space for your business email communications and data.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> What ports do I need to use for Email Hosting? </h5>
              <p>Use the following ports for Email Hosting: IMAP (Port 143 or 993 for secure SSL), POP3 (Port 110 or 995 for secure SSL), and SMTP (Port 25 or 587 for secure SSL).</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> Can I create mailing lists? </h5>
              <p>Yes, you can create mailing lists with our Email Hosting. Utilize this feature to efficiently manage and send emails to specific groups or audiences for your business communication needs.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5> What is your SPAM policy? </h5>
              <p>Our SPAM policy ensures a secure and clean email environment. Strict measures are taken to prevent, detect, and eliminate spam, maintaining a high-quality email service.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
